// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3021 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 188d26b3-1598-5539-a60a-ec0a10c46cd0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
